    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. i've heard some people say it's basically a death sentence for local shops in towns like mine, while others say it'll actually help because people will have more money to spend in the community. what do the studies actually show? is there a consensus on whether it's a net positive or negative for small towns?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
